      "writtenOn": "2026-05-25T05:51:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The traffic is not bi-directional, this tunnel is only used as decapsulation purpose - decap IPinIP traffic destinated to this local device with any source IP.\n\nThis PR is needed by SONiC-VPP project, which is a kvm-based virtual SONiC environment that uses VPP as dataplane. And this new mode is to simulatethe SONiC IPinIP dataplane forwardin behavior.",
      "parentUuid": "df7f1ea9_c92bf441",
      "revId": "8e394e0e53798b495330630d0ede3ec3c49c5b8c",
      "serverId": "6d2eb258-4fe2-443e-8a38-ca81da23d4c2"
